{"type":"message","id":"485e74df","parentId":"6a53329d","timestamp":"2026-02-23T18:19:04.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Responding to safety concerns**\n\nI should respond with concern and ask how I can help, especially considering the dangerous incident mentioned. It’s important to provide immediate, high-level safety guidance: contacting emergency services, ensuring the scene is safe, and providing general first aid steps without giving specific medical advice. I can mention that in India, the emergency numbers are 112 for general emergencies and 108 for ambulances. I'll also seek consent to share information with emergency services and ask for their location.**Responding to user needs**\n\nI need to greet the user and ask what they want to do next. Since they sent a new message, I’ll respond with clear and helpful action steps in a bullet list. There’s no need to use any tools right now. I’ll also ask for confirmation if they want me to contact authorities or draft a message for someone. Including any necessary escalation steps will be important in my response. Let’s get to it!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"That sounds like an urgent situation. If you’re with the patient right now, please call emergency services immediately (India: dial 112 or 108 for ambulance) and provide your exact location. \n\nIf safe to do so, you can: \n- Check responsiveness and airway/breathing; if unresponsive and not breathing normally, begin CPR if trained. \n- Place a clean cloth over the bleeding and apply firm, direct pressure; avoid removing any helmet or bulky objects. \n- Keep them still and monitor for changes while waiting for help.\n\nTell me your exact location and I can help draft a quick message to emergency services or someone on-site."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":10168,"output":649,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10817,"cost":{"input":-10168,"output":-649,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-10817}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771870730701}}
